name: Paraguana Colors #6
description:
Description: Venezuelan photographers always have said that Paraguana is our New York City, I was skeptic because I've never been in NYC but I know the importance of that city for the global community of photographers... So these are my photograhs concerning that first visit to that magic place, because that's what you find in Paraguaná: magic light and magic colors. 

"Casa Las Virtudes" (The house of the virtues) know in Paraguana as the house of the famous venezuelan architect Graziano Gasparini (RIP), it's amazing how surrounded by the desert of the Peninsula, you can find a beautiful yellow house aligned perfectly with the natural landscape...
